  "texts": [
    "Often one uses a pre-trained library for this.",
    "Computing numerical representations of the text: bag-of-word models",
    "The previous steps have transformed a raw text into a sequence of tokens.",
    "Since the text corpus contains a defined vocabulary of unique tokens, this delivers the encoding of the raw text into a sequence of integers (representing the identifier of each token), see Figure 1.",
